        "en": "Set ambilight temperature to [[temperature]]",
        "nl": "Zet ambilight temperatuur naar [[temperature]]"
      },
      "hint": {
        "en": "Use this card to set the temperature of the ambilight. A higher value is a warmer temperature.",
